140
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,720
What about you?

141
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,360
Isn't it all because you
canceled our engagement?

142
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,720
Isn't it because you
wanted to find a safer choice?

143
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,120
You need to provide evidence
when you speak.

144
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,320
It's in my dreams.

145
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,040
Your evidence is in the dreams?

146
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,240
Mine is in the eyes of the people.

147
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,080
Why do you dream of me every day?

148
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:14,400
Is it because your thoughts
in the day become dreams at night?

149
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,960
Yes.

150
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,960
But my intuition tells me,

151
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,680
you should belong to me.

152
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,240
Farewell, Your Highness.

153
00:08:37,888 --> 00:08:39,093
(Tolerance)

154
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,440
(Shame on you, Camper Pei.)

155
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,080
Liu Yueqing.

